## 🛠️ OKF Tooling &amp; Value Added

This bundle was enhanced using the [`dnx okf`](https://github.com/devlooped/okf) toolchain:

| Feature                  | Description                                                                 |
|--------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Graph Model**          | All Markdown links → directed edges automatically                           |
| **Centrality Analytics** | PageRank + degree metrics highlight the most structurally important ideas   |
| **Validation**           | `dnx okf check` verifies frontmatter, structure, and link integrity         |
| **Visualization**        | Self-contained interactive `index.html` (node-link diagram). [Live hosted version](https://www.cazzulino.com/the-law/) |

### Top-ranked concepts (by structural importance)

1. `legal-plunder/definition` — the heart of the thesis
2. `the-law` — primary entry point
3. `true-law/proper-sphere`
4. `fundamental-principles/law-as-organization-of-defense`
5. `fundamental-principles/natural-rights`

